 <center> 
  <h1><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Adaptation Rules</font></h1> 
 </center> 
 
<p><br>
  <font size="4" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">An Adaptation Rule Language</font></p>
<ul>
  <li><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">The author has decided to use 
    the database rule formalism &quot;Condition Action&quot; rules</font></li>
  <li><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Condition Action simply means 
    that the the action is done when the condition has been made true</font></li>
  <li><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Additionally, the author has used 
    SQL syntax in order to create easily readable rules</font></li>
</ul>
